name: About Me
body:
### **About Me:**
My name is Pei Ling, I am currently a senior at Burton High School residing in San Francisco, California. I was born in GuangZhou, China but came to America at the age of 2. I am creating this portfolio to hold all the works I have done over the years of AoAME, Academy of Arts, Media, Entertainment. Keeping a portfolio like this will not only enable to me keep my work for future hands but also for others to view my work. Enjoy!
